{"tid":524985,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"寸爆！列查積隻狗仔叫「槍手」","createTime":"2018-01-10T07:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T08:37:13.000Z","uid":109491,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63bfd7c70034fa9af1923407a4cc0999baecffe0","tid":524985,"uid":109491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=FpeAYFKsRB0rqWTOSL4xgwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=1dedbe9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】諾定咸森林後衛列查積借「群眾壓力」逼使太太批准他養狗一事，終如願，並已把小狗命名為「槍手」。<br />\n<br />\n英冠諾定咸森林在上周的足總盃以4:2淘汰阿仙奴晉級，隊中的美國後衛列查積（Eric Lichaj）梅開二度，成為球隊贏波英雄，列查積周二在Twitter就上載一位家庭新成員的照片，就是一頭愛犬，並已把它命名為「槍手」（Gunner），相信現在最反對列查積養狗的應該是阿仙奴的球迷吧？<br />\n<br />\n這位29歲美國國腳一直希望在家中養狗，他的太太在對阿仙奴賽前就提出了一個「不可能的條件」，假如列查積在比賽中射入3球的話，就會批准他養狗。不知道列查積是不是真的很想養狗，在這場比賽中非常落力，最終射入了兩球，可是這仍未能達到太太的要求。<br />\n<br />\n列查積最後唯有「使橫手」，在Twitter上動員森林的球迷向他的太太「拖壓」，希望能夠令她能夠破例，最終列查積亦得償所願把小狗帶回家。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"04280406390a5a4b283a88f3a592dc978787f866","tid":524985,"uid":109491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"Eric Lichaj's named his new dog &quot;Gunner&quot; after he scored two goals to help Forest defeat Arsenal in the FA Cup.Unverified account<br />\n<br />\nEric Lichaj<br />\n@ericlichaj<br />\n<br />\nWanted to show everyone the newest member of the Lichaj family.... Gunner. Thank you everyone for for pushing @KatPerko in the right direction! #erichasadog<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DTIJgVrXcAMWBXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDTIJgVrXcAMWBXH.jpg&h=321381a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42aad2283ed1cf883a8d486f2647756914afccf4","tid":524985,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"讓個12碼佢射就完美"},{"pid":"49e6c2e702de3a6c76d3a7f5fea6c5486a500b62","tid":524985,"uid":93